<template>
    <b-card :header="`Leitora: ${ selectedmodel.model }`">
        <b-card-text class="text-center">
            <barcode :value="barcodevalue">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="90" height="90" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M19 8.025v-3.025h2v3.181c-.482-.114-.982-.181-1.5-.181l-.5.025zm5 1.791v-4.816h-1v4.028c.359.231.693.494 1 .788zm-7-1.316v-3.5h-1v4.028c.316-.202.649-.382 1-.528zm-13 8.5h2v-12h-2v12zm9-2.5c0-1.271.37-2.452 1-3.453v-6.047h-3v12h2.5c-.321-.77-.5-1.614-.5-2.5zm-5 2.5h1v-12h-1v12zm-8 0h2v-12h-2v12zm19.5-7c-2.483 0-4.5 2.015-4.5 4.5s2.017 4.5 4.5 4.5 4.5-2.015 4.5-4.5-2.017-4.5-4.5-4.5zm2.122 3.085l-1.414 1.415 1.414 1.414-.708.708-1.414-1.415-1.414 1.414-.707-.708 1.414-1.414-1.414-1.414.707-.708 1.414 1.414 1.414-1.414.708.708z"/>
                </svg>
            </barcode>
        </b-card-text>
        <hr/>
        <b-card-text>
            Selecione a opção abaixo para configurar seu leitor de código de barras.
        </b-card-text>
        <b-card-text>
            <b-form-select v-model="barcodevalue" :options="selectedmodel.commands"></b-form-select>
        </b-card-text>            
        <b-alert variant="warning" :show="selectedmodelcommandsalert.show">
            {{ selectedmodelcommandsalert.description }}
        </b-alert>            
    </b-card>
</template>

<script>
import { mapGetters } from 'vuex'
export default {

    name: 'BarcodeConfig',

    props: {
        model: ''
    },

    data() {
        return {
            barcodevalue: ''

        }
    },

    computed: {

        ...mapGetters(['gtxbarcodebymodel']),

         selectedmodel() {
            return this.gtxbarcodebymodel(this.model)
        },

        selectedmodelcommands() {
            return this.selectedmodel.commands.find(f => f.value == this.barcodevalue) || ''
        },

        selectedmodelcommandsalert() {
            return { 
                show: (this.selectedmodelcommands) ? this.selectedmodelcommands.description!=='' : false,
                description: (this.selectedmodelcommands) ? this.selectedmodelcommands.description : ''
            }
        }
    }
    
}
</script>
